{
  "abstract": "Several types of insect traps are being used by entomologists at ICRISAT in their pest-management research on sorghum, millet, groundnut, pigeonpea, and chickpea. The various traps most of which have been developed or adapted at ICRISAT, are described. The utility of these traps for monitoring and pest management is discussed.",
